<HEADER>
<TABLE_HEADER Style Settings>
<form action="~script_name~?menu=setup&action=settings_styles" method="POST">
<input type="hidden" name="action" value="update">

<FONT_BODY>
From here you can change the appearance of your Member Control Panel.  You can change 
things such as the font, and color scheme of your Member Control Panel.  Feel free to 
change any of the information below, and once done click on the <i>Update Settings</i> 
button to save the changes.
</font><br><br><LINE>

<FONT_HEADER Header Table Style>
<FONT_BODY>
From here you can change the appearance of all header tables in your Member Control Panel.  The 
header table is what is shown in the blue box at the top of the page which says <i>Style Settings</i>.
</font><br><br>

<blockquote><table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=2 width=80%>
<tr>
	<td nowrap><FONT_BODY>Background Color:</font></td>
	<td nowrap><input type="text" name="table_bgcolor" size=10 value="~TABLE_BGCOLOR~"></td>
</tr><tr>
	<td nowrap><FONT_BODY>Font Face:</font></td>
	<td nowrap><input type="text" name="table_font_face" size=15 value="~TABLE_FONT_FACE~"></td>
</tr><tr>
	<td nowrap><FONT_BODY>Font Size:</font></td>
	<td nowrap><input type="text" name="table_font_size" size=8 value="~TABLE_FONT_SIZE~"></td>
</tr><tr>
	<td nowrap><FONT_BODY>Font Color:</font></td>
	<td nowrap><input type="text" name="table_font_color" size=10 value="~TABLE_FONT_COLOR~"></td>
</tr></table></blockquote><br><br>


<FONT_HEADER Header Font Style>
<FONT_BODY>
From here you can change the appearance of the header font in your Member Control Panel.  The 
header font is the large font to the several sections on each page.  For example, just above there 
is a header font which says, <i>Header Font Style</i>.
</font><br><br>

<blockquote><table border=0 cellspacing=1 cellpadding=2 width=80%>
<tr>
